name: Sword Art Online Fan Token
description: Greatest project in VR  SAO VR MMORPG aims to give you the experience of another world "ISEKAI". The project intends to gather all the VR Gear companies to improve and design Aincrad the floating castle in a VR environment that you can access from your own home. You will be able to earn SAO in game while playing and trade items on the auction house for SAO, the Token will be able to transfer from your game account to any wallet or market.
